{"tid":561267,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"美國六大情報機構共同呼籲美國用戶別用華為產品","createTime":"2018-02-15T00:45:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-16T13:12:08.000Z","uid":37524,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"bdec8ea57dd9fcfb90d9bc06d4ee5ea2eddaf227","tid":561267,"uid":37524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T00:45:36.000Z","msg":"繼疑似透過政治力量迫使美國前兩大電信商Verizon與AT&amp;T，都放棄協助中國手機品牌(Huawei)代銷手機之後，美國六大情報機構共同呼籲，美國用戶不要用華為的產品或是服務，除再度對於華為手機產品入美投下不信任票外，也展現護衛國家安全的決心。此舉無非讓積極拓展美國市場的華為，二度受到重挫。<br />\n<br />\n美國時間本月13日，美國六大情報機構主管共同參與參議院情報委員會的聽證會，會中他們異口同聲的建議美國消費者不要使用華為的產品，同時也對中興(ZTE)的產品表達了不信任。<br />\n<br />\n聽證會中，FBI(聯邦調查局)局長Christopher Wray表示，「允許任何對我們有不同價值觀的外國政府承擔義務的公司或實體，在我們的電信通信領域發揮影響力，那種風險讓我們深感擔憂。」他進一步指出，「那樣會讓他們有能力對我們施加壓力或控制我們的電信基礎服務，而且也讓他們有能力來惡意修改或竊取我們的資訊，甚至可以讓他們有能力師實施無法偵測到的間諜行為。」<br />\n<br />\n出席參議院聽證會的美國六大情報機構，除了FBI之外，還有CIA(美國中央情報局)局長Mike Pompeo、國家情報局(National Intelligence)局長Dan Coats、國防情報局(Defense Intelligence Agency)局長Robert Ashley、NSA(國家安全局)局長 Michael Rogers上將以及國家地理空間情報局(National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency)Robert Cardillo。<br />\n<br />\n華為一直以來都相當積極進軍美國市場，雖然他們的手機產品目前沒有辦法透過美國電信商代為銷售(電信商代銷手機是美國地區智慧型手機主要銷售管道)，仍可在官方線上商店、指定線上平台以及授權的經銷商購買得到。而在美國六大情報機構聯合呼籲之後，會不會對於華為(及中興)相關產品在美國的銷售造成進一步阻力，以及華為方面對此事的回應，都很値得持續觀察。<br />\n<br />\n(中時電子報<a href=\"http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180214001387-260412\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20180214001387-260412&d=tC8wHLE06i9okBTfUkldosmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=63f9ab2d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180214001387-260412</a>)<br />\n<br />\n文章來源：CNBC<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cnbc.com/2018/02/13/chinas-hauwei-top-us-intelligence-chiefs-caution-americans-away.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2018%2F02%2F13%2Fchinas-hauwei-top-us-intelligence-chiefs-caution-americans-away.html&d=tC8wHLE06i9okBTfUkldosmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=e5fd06bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cnbc.com/2018/02/13/chinas-hauwei-top-us-intelligence-chiefs-caution-americans-away.html</a>"},{"pid":"24ad5b5a348617122971b16ae15a85a90a1e4c66","tid":561267,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T00:47:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af5d55b903d6db7c6313658ab1f8ce9f118bcfbf","tid":561267,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T01:57:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e94e9b4ce03cb79266ee577ca9746c508793264","tid":561267,"uid":30169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T02:38:38.000Z","msg":"點解唔直頭禁賣"},{"pid":"65a343619bb6d4d75971f94f0756f7be8ecda9e5","tid":561267,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T03:07:31.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"d26fea3f2ade5cc52cb1f4543f4833ed25453025","tid":561267,"uid":65144,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T03:42:37.000Z","msg":"用小米好過"},{"pid":"a19c6fe6b04e6b86ae5d77447f438dd097f84538","tid":561267,"uid":48234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d26fea3f2ade5cc52cb1f4543f4833ed25453025","tid":561267,"uid":65144,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T03:42:37.000Z","msg":"用小米好過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T04:48:00.000Z","msg":"咪又係一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f035ebb8fc6f02e1ab07aed938665a4b79590b7d","tid":561267,"uid":37688,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T09:30:09.000Z","msg":"軍方背景公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57af31139d22617cc4c764efdcd1b34e5f3a6006","tid":561267,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T09